            <zone h='98546' id='6' type-v2='layout-basic' w='98118' x='941' y='727'>
              <zone forceUpdate='true' h='23273' id='3' type-v2='text' w='98118' x='941' y='727'>
                <formatted-text>
                  <run bold='true' fontsize='18' underline='true'>Deciding to Study Away and Selecting a Location</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;&#10;&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run bold='true' fontsize='15'>Q1: How would you rate the importance of the following factors in deciding to study away?</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run italic='true'>Note: This question asks students to identify factors that influenced their decision to study away in general, not at their location specifically. This question was not shown to first year away students.</run>
                </formatted-text>
                <zone-style>
                  <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                  <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                  <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                  <format attr='margin' value='4' />
